  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hello! I'm your relationship facilitation guide. I can help you analyze relationship patterns, prepare for sessions, identify concerns, and suggest interventions for the relationships you oversee. Which relationship would you like to discuss, or would you like an overview of all your current cases?",
